original_title: Dave of the Dead: Deadly Delivery
overview: With thousands of Spacejacks orders delivered and thousands more to go, well-meaning space zombie Dave and his always-voracious companion Num-Num the carnivorous plant, face their most challenging fast-food delivery ever - to the Grimm Reaper himself. As they race to deliver their order before the 30 space minutes are up the monster duo discovers that an epic destiny awaits them. This Halloween, laugh 'til you coffin with Dave Of The Dead Deadly Delivery.
tagline: It takes brains to deliver on time.
title: Dave of the Dead: Deadly Delivery
